<html>

<head>
  <title>Stephi_Designer_App</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/Test.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/Basic_info.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div class="k">
    <h2>Basic information form</h2>
    <br>
    <form name="form" method="POST" action="/FormController/save">
      <div class="form-group">
        <% for(let i=0; i < perf.length;i++){%>
        First name:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="firstname" value="<%= perf[i].firstname %>" placeholder="Please enter your firstname"
          required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        Last name:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="lastname" placeholder="Please enter your lastname" required value="<%= perf[i].lastname %>">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%if(perf[i].playname.length == 0){%>
        Play name:<br>
        <select name="playname">
          <option value="">--Select--</option>
          <%for(let k=0; k < playDetails.length; k++){%>
          <option value="<%=playDetails[k].playname%>">
            <%=playDetails[k].playname%>
          </option>
          <%}%>
          <%}%>
        </select>
      </div>
      Play name:<br>
      <%if(perf[i].playname.length != 0){%>
      <input class="form-control" type="text" name="playname" required value=<%=perf[i].playname %>><br>
      <%}%>
      <div class="form-group">
        Play date:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="date" name="playdate" placeholder="Please enter the play date" required value="<%= perf[i].playdate %>">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        Character Name:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="charactername" placeholder="Enter your Charactername" required
          value="<%= perf[i].charactername %>">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        Phone Number:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="tel" name="phonenumber" placeholder="123-456-7890" pattern="[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{4}"
          required value="<%= perf[i].phonenumber %>">
      </div>
      May we text you?<br>
      <input id='CheckedYes' type="radio" name="textchoice" value="yes"> Yes<br>
      <input id='CheckedNo' type="radio" name="textchoice" value="no"> No<br><br>
      <div class="form-group">
        University email Address:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="email" name="email1" placeholder="Enter your E-MAIL" required value="<%= perf[i].email %>">
      </div>
      "I understand that I must check my Northwest student email DAILY as requests for fitting appointments will be
      sent to that email. I will respond to a fitting request as soon as possible. I understand that failing to check
      my university email does not excuse me from missing a fitting appointment. Missed appointments will be
      rescheduled at the discretion of the Costume Shop."<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="agreement" value="iagree" required> Yes, I understand.<br><br>
      Dominant Hand: <br>
      <%if(perf[i].dominanthand.length == 0){%>
      <select name="dominanthand" class="form-control">
        <option value="">--Please select--</option>
        <option value="Right">Right</option>
        <option value="Left">Left</option>
      </select>
      <%}%>
      <%if(perf[i].dominanthand.length != 0){%>
      <input class="form-control" type="text" name="dominanthand" required value=<%=perf[i].dominanthand %>><br>
      <%}%>

      <!-- <input type="checkbox" name="dominanthand" value="right" > Right<br>
    <input type="checkbox" name="dominanthand" value="left"> Left<br><br> -->
      <div class="form-group">
        Height:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="heught" placeholder="Enter height in feet" required value="<%= perf[i].height %>">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        Estimated Weight: <br>
        <input class="form-control" type="number" name="estimatedweight" placeholder="Enter weight in pounds" required
          value="<%= perf[i].estimatedweight %>">
      </div>
      Corrective Eyewear:<br>
      <input type="radio" name="eyewearchoice" value="none"> None<br>
      <input type="radio" name="eyewearchoice" value="glasses"> Glasses<br>
      <input type="radio" name="eyewearchoice" value="contacts"> Contacts<br>
      <input type="radio" name="eyewearchoice" value="withoutglasses"> I wear glasses but can perform without them<br><br>
      <div class="form-group">
        Hair color and length:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="hair" placeholder="Enter your Haircolor & Length" required value="<%= perf[i].hair %>"><br>
        Facial Hair: color, length, and growth time:<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="facialhai" placeholder="Enter your Facialhair Color, Length & Growth time"
          required value="<%= perf[i].facialhai %>">
      </div>
      I understand that I may not permanently change the color, length, or style of my hair between casting and
      performance without the express permission of both the Costume Designer and Artistic Director.<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="hairagreement" value="iagree" required> Yes, I understand.<br><br>
      Do you have pierced ears?<br>
      <input type="radio" name="earschoice" value="yes"> Yes<br>
      <input type="radio" name="earschoice" value="no"> No<br><br>
      <div class="form-group">
        Do you have any other piercings? How many and where?<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="otherpiercings" placeholder="Enter details of other piercing"
          required value="<%= perf[i].otherpiercings %>"><br>
        Do you have any tattoos?<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="tattoos" placeholder="Enter details of tatoos" required value="<%= perf[i].tattoos %>">
      </div>
      "I understand that if I have tattos I must provide my own tattoo cover makeup if asked. I understand that if I
      have piercings I may be asked to remove them or provide my own clear spacer during performances. I understand
      that I am not allowed to permanently alter my body with additional tattoos, piercings, etc. between casting and
      performance."<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="tattooagreement" value="iagree" required> Yes, I understand.<br><br>
      COMMENTS ABOUT THE BODY (OR COSTUME) OF ANY PERFORMER (YOURSELF INCLUDED) WILL NOT BE TOLERATED FROM ANY
      PERFORMER OR MEMBER OF THE PRODUCTION STAFF.<br>
      <div class="form-group">
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="comments" required value="<%= perf[i].comments %>"><br>
        Shoes: <br>
        <%if(perf[i].shoes.length == 0){%>
        <select name="shoes" class="form-control">
          <option value="">--Please select--</option>
          <option value="5.5">5.5</option>
          <option value="6.0">6.0</option>
          <option value="6.5">6.5</option>
          <option value="7.0">7.0</option>
          <option value="7.5">7.5</option>
          <option value="8.0">8.0</option>
          <option value="8.5">8.5</option>
          <option value="9.0">9.0</option>
          <option value="10.0">10.0</option>
          <option value="10.5">10.5</option>
          <option value="11.0">11.0</option>
          <option value="11.5">11.5</option>
          <option value="12.0">12.0</option>
          <option value="12.5">12.5</option>
          <option value="13.0">13.0</option>
          <option value="13.5">13.5</option>
          <option value="14.0">14.0</option>
          <option value="14.5">14.5</option>
          <option value="15.0">15.0</option>

        </select><br>
        <%}%>
        <%if(perf[i].shoes.length != 0){%>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="shoes" required value=<%=perf[i].shoes %>><br>
        <%}%>
        Dance Shoes: Size and Type<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="danceshoes" required value=<%=perf[i].danceshoes %>>
      </div>
      Shirt <br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="xs"> XS<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="s"> S<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="m"> M<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="l"> L<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="xl"> XL<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="xxl"> XXL<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="xxxl"> XXXL<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="shirtsize" value="other"> Other<br><br>
      <div class="form-group">
        Pants <br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="pants" value="<%= perf[i].pants %>"><br>
        <!-- Bra size<br>
    <input class="form-control" type="text" name="brasize"><br> -->
        Ring<br>
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="ring" value="<%= perf[i].ring %>">
      </div>
      Are you allergic to any of the following?<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="allergy" value="Fabric/fiber"> Fabric/fiber<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="allergy" value="Detergent"> Detergent<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="allergy" value="Environmental"> Environmental<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="allergy" value="Fragrance"> Fragrance<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="allergy" value="Metal"> Metal<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="allergy" value="No allergies"> No allergies<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="allergy" value="Other"> Other: <div class="form-group"><input class="form-control"
          type="text" name="other"></div>
      If you have allergies, please give specific details here.<br>
      <div class="form-group">
        <input class="form-control" type="text" name="allergies" value="<%= perf[i].allergies %>"></div><br>
      <br>
      <h2>Physical Limitations</h2>
      <p>If you have any illness, injury, prosthesis, or physical limitation that might affect the comfort or fit of
        your costume, please discuss this privately with the costume designer. Some examples:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>knee brace</li>
        <li>scoliosis</li>
        <li>asymmetry (one limb significantly longer or larger than the other)</li>
        <li>arthritis/dexterity problems</li>
        <li>need specific undergarments for comfort or modesty</li>
        <li> prefer compression tights</li>
        <li>use of prosthesis</li>
        <li>use of mobility aid</li>
        <li>unable to sweat/regulate body temperature</li>
        <li>need sweatguards</li>
        <li>specific shoe style needed</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Please only disclose as much information as you are comfortable with and is relevant to the fit and comfort of
        your costume. This will insure that the costume designer can make you look your best!</p>
      <%if(perf[i].firstname.length == 0 ){%>
      <div class="b"><input type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn btn-primary"></div>
      <%}%>
    </form>
    <p>
      <%=perf[i].firstname%>
    </p>
    <%if(perf[i].firstname.length != 0 ){%>
    <div class="b"><button value="HomePage" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="goToHomePage()">HomePage</button></div>
    <%}%>

    <%}%>



  </div>
</body>